/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你突然打醒我"},{"pid":"bd7b9d2c8265d66dc6ff6d894aca015ba5a24898","tid":259810,"uid":108039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T09:41:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>搵唔搵番佢好</blockquote><br />\n你咩都唔講, 點知搵唔搵返佢</blockquote><br />\n分開左幾日 掛住佢 和平分手</blockquote><br />\n你提出定係佢提出? 邊個提出都好影響? 仲有既然要分手, 何必到呢家仲在意?</blockquote><br />\n要挽留應該係佢提出分手時挽留, 唔係等呢家。</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n宜家係我退開左一步睇到自己有咩問題</blockquote><br />\n你睇到自己有咩問題, 同可以改到呢個問題係兩件事。<br />\n比如, 經常遲到, 同能夠改到遲到習慣係兩件事"},{"pid":"1adc50fcfe0d3d60685a2e1ca56f04d0ebbf03fa","tid":259810,"uid":46515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T09:41:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢為左個ex唔要我</blockquote><br />\n不如你諗下佢由始至終有冇鐘意過你仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我感覺之前係有。 係咪追到手真係會全部野都變曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}